Product description

By choosing this pair of excellent quality Surgical Steel CZ crystal earrings, it attracts a lot of attention and lets everyone acknowledge your sense of style and fashion with these high sparkling cubic zirconia stud earrings. These earrings are enclosed with secure push backs to keep them in place with additional stopper push back to keep your earrings securely in place.

Size: These earrings are available in 7 sizes
Each pack includes: One pair of these adorable stud earrings
Color:This style is available in multiple colors to choose from
